Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琉加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跳得幅度這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道已經不疼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然會疼  但是她在靠意志堅持著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離下一首曲子還有3分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請快點更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女僕之星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  這就是你的下一套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…你這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來幫幫我  我的粉絲在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是真正的職業偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琉加小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  琉加小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琉加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要最後一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到她能堅持到最後  真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  可愛的女僕小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近有沒有見過一個一臉窮酸像的男性管家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基佬伯  你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照這樣子看  你也是琉加小姐的粉絲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋  你為什麼知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你就是那個欠債管家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:19:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然敢利用我對女性的愛好假扮成女性來使我露出破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太無恥了  太無恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡見到你也是命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了得到三千院家的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在這裡將你打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我是偶像剋星961SP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:16.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（偶像大師中765事務所的對手 長相是蓋塔1+2）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最愛錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個不知悔改的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你妨礙到琉加小姐的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是唱最後那首歌時要出場的人偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  怎麼還在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我過來  該你上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:36.16,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  不對  你們抓錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一首  要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太可愛了  琉加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:49.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（同樣捏自AKB粉絲的應援口號）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像最後都會有很多的玩偶一邊出出進進
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那機器人幹什麼呢  你快點想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,NO  我也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（捏自鐵人28的控制器）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你那麼使勁踢它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點讓他下場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  他好像沒有戴耳麥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就誰把他踢下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我  適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來  總算局勢控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  該上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:20:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  是這種安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早告訴我們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的女裝版還真是合適到可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有沒有  該我們說謝謝才對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  好有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你乾脆做女人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯  一會兒要不要穿這個試試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧來吧  沒準很合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琉加你是怎麼看待小颯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.19,0:24:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼看待的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N…NICE CUTIE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.94,0:24:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C…CUTIE MATE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才想問你什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
